Step 3 ‚Äì Install Deeb for Local Data Persistence
Now let‚Äôs get to the fun stuff. We will need to store chat messages so we can see previous conversations!

Deeb gives us MongoDB-style persistence but stored locally in JSON files. It‚Äôs a NoSQL no-fuss way that we can persist data with minimal setup in a Rust Application. It‚Äôs embedded nature is perfect for this app - keeping all our chat logs local and readable.

cargo add deeb
